            Subscribing to the ak-emsc Internet Mail List Server

   Because of the scope and complexity of statewide EMS for Children
   (EMSC) projects, the Section of Community Health and EMS is sponsoring
   an internet mail list server dedicated to EMSC activities in Alaska.

   To join this free list, send an e-mail message to:

   list.manager@list.state.ak.us

   The body of the message should be:

   subscribe ak-emsc

   We will be using this service to distribute informational updates and
   hope that people who have subscribed to the list also will use it as a
   forum for sharing information on best practices, local EMSC activities,
   and other issues likely to be interesting to others on the list.

   Although we hope to use electronic forms of communication to great
   advantage with this project, we will continue to send EMSC project
   related correspondence and other materials via the U.S. Postal Service
   when appropriate or necessary.



